## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [fbn6-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Smaller rosettes, reduction in rosette fresh weight to less than half; late flowering under long-day photoperiods, though not under short-day conditions; paler leaves with reduced chlorophyll, Chl a/Chl b ratio was increased. Increased glutathione levels and  increased tolerance to cadmium.
